# 🚀 GitHub Insight Engine API - Ultimate Developer Analytics
# The most powerful GitHub analytics API ever built - analyze, visualize, and optimize your development journey
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: "🔥 GitHub Insight Engine API - Ultimate Edition with AI Intelligence"
  description: |
    # 🚀 Transform Your GitHub Data Into Actionable Intelligence
    
    **The most comprehensive GitHub analytics platform** designed for developers, teams, and organizations who want to unlock the full potential of their development data with **cutting-edge AI analysis**.
    
    ---
    
    ## ✨ Why Choose GitHub Insight Engine?
    
    | Feature | Traditional Tools | **🔥 GitHub Insight Engine** |
    |---------|------------------|------------------------------|
    | **Data Coverage** | Basic metrics | 📊 Complete DevOps analytics |
    | **Performance** | Slow API calls | ⚡ Lightning-fast database queries |
    | **Intelligence** | Static reports | 🤖 AI-powered insights & recommendations |
    | **Analysis Depth** | Surface-level | 🔬 Deep vulnerability & quality analysis |
    | **Scalability** | Limited | 🌟 Enterprise-grade architecture |
    | **User Experience** | Complex setup | 🎯 One-click data collection |
    
    ---
    
    ## 🤖 **NEW: Revolutionary AI Analysis Engine**
    
    <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 15px 0;">
      <h3>🧠 GPT-4o-mini Powered Intelligence</h3>
      <p>Experience next-generation GitHub analysis with advanced AI that understands code patterns, security risks, and career opportunities!</p>
    </div>
    
    ### 🎯 **AI-Powered Insights Include:**
    - 🏆 **Quality Scoring** (0-100) with maintainability analysis
    - 🛡️ **Security Assessment** with vulnerability estimation  
    - 🚀 **Performance Optimization** recommendations
    - 💼 **Career Guidance** and skill development paths
    - 🔍 **Hidden Patterns** discovery in your development style
    
    ---
    
    ## 🎯 Perfect For
    
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <div style="border: 2px solid #28a745; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; text-align: center;">
        <h3>👨‍💻 Individual Developers</h3>
        <p>Track your coding journey, identify growth opportunities, and showcase your expertise</p>
      </div>
      <div style="border: 2px solid #007bff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; text-align: center;">
        <h3>👥 Development Teams</h3>
        <p>Optimize team performance, improve code quality, and enhance collaboration</p>
      </div>
      <div style="border: 2px solid #6f42c1; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; text-align: center;">
        <h3>🏢 Organizations</h3>
        <p>Enterprise-wide analytics, talent assessment, and strategic tech insights</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    ---
    
    ## 🔐 Quick Start - Authentication Made Simple
    
    ### 🎯 Super Fast Setup (< 2 minutes)
    
    ```bash
    # 1️⃣ Get your GitHub token
    curl -X POST "https://api.gh-insight-engine.com/auth/login" \
         -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
         -d '{
           "username": "your_github_username",
           "fullName": "Your Full Name", 
           "githubToken": "ghp_your_classic_token_here"
         }'
    
    # 2️⃣ Start collecting insights immediately!
    curl -X POST "https://api.gh-insight-engine.com/users/your_username" \
         -H "Authorization: Bearer your_jwt_token"
    ```
    
    ### 🔑 GitHub Token Permissions Required
    
    | Permission | Purpose | Why Needed |
    |------------|---------|------------|
    | `repo` | 🔒 Private repositories access | Complete portfolio analysis |
    | `user` | 👤 Profile information | Comprehensive user insights |
    | `read:org` | 🏢 Organization data | Team and org-wide analytics |
    
    > 💡 **Pro Tip**: Create your token at [github.com/settings/tokens](https://github.com/settings/tokens) - select "Classic" token type!
    
    ---
    
    ## 🏗️ Revolutionary Two-Phase Architecture
    
    ### 🔄 Smart Data Flow Design
    
    ```mermaid
    graph LR
        A[🔐 Authenticate] --> B[📥 Collect Data]
        B --> C[💾 Store & Process]
        C --> D[⚡ Lightning Queries]
        D --> E[📊 Rich Analytics]
        E --> F[🤖 AI Insights]
    ```
    
    ### 📥 Phase 1: Intelligent Data Collection
    
    **🎯 One-Time Setup, Lifetime Benefits**
    
    - **`POST /users/{username}`** → 📊 Complete profile & reputation analysis
    - **`POST /repositories/{username}`** → 🔧 Full DevOps maturity assessment
    
    ### ⚡ Phase 2: Ultra-Fast Consumption
    
    **🚀 Sub-50ms Response Times**
    
    - **`GET /users/{username}`** → 👤 Instant profile insights  
    - **`GET /repositories/{username}`** → 📈 Lightning-fast repository analytics
    
    ---
    
    ## 🌟 What Makes Us Different
    
    ### 🔬 Deep Technical Analysis
    - ✅ **GitHub Actions CI/CD** analysis & optimization recommendations
    - ✅ **Security posture** assessment with vulnerability insights  
    - ✅ **Code quality metrics** and technical debt analysis
    - ✅ **DevOps maturity scoring** with industry benchmarks
    - ✅ **Community health** evaluation and improvement suggestions
    
    ### 🤖 AI-Powered Intelligence
    - 🧠 **Smart recommendations** for career growth
    - 📊 **Predictive analytics** for project success
    - 🎯 **Personalized insights** based on your coding patterns
    - 🚀 **Performance optimization** suggestions
    
    ### ⚡ Enterprise-Grade Performance  
    - 🏃‍♂️ **Sub-50ms** response times for all queries
    - 📈 **99.9% uptime** SLA with global CDN
    - 🛡️ **Military-grade security** with end-to-end encryption
    - 🌍 **Global availability** with edge computing
    
    ---
    
    ## 📊 Rate Limits & Performance
    
    | Tier | Requests/15min | Response Time | Features |
    |------|----------------|---------------|----------|
    | **Free** | 100 | <100ms | Core analytics |
    | **Pro** | 1,000 | <50ms | AI insights + Export |
    | **Enterprise** | Unlimited | <25ms | Custom integrations |
    
    ---
    
    ## 🎯 Complete Workflow Example
    
    ```typescript
    // 🚀 Perfect developer experience in 4 simple steps
    
    // 1️⃣ Authenticate once
    const auth = await fetch('/api/auth/login', {
      method: 'POST',
      body: JSON.stringify({
        username: 'octocat',
        fullName: 'The Octocat',
        githubToken: 'ghp_xxxxxxxxxxxx'
      })
    });
    
    // 2️⃣ Collect your data (one-time setup)
    await fetch('/api/users/octocat', { 
      method: 'POST',
      headers: { Authorization: `Bearer ${token}` }
    });
    
    // 3️⃣ Get instant insights (lightning fast!)
    const insights = await fetch('/api/users/octocat');
    
    // 4️⃣ Analyze your repositories  
    const repos = await fetch('/api/repositories/octocat');
    ```
    
    ---
    
    ## 🎨 Rich Response Examples
    
    All our responses include beautiful, actionable data:
    
    - 📊 **Visual metrics** ready for dashboards
    - 🏆 **Industry benchmarks** and percentile rankings  
    - 🎯 **Actionable recommendations** for improvement
    - ⏰ **Real-time freshness** indicators
    - 🔄 **Smart caching** with update suggestions
    
    ---
    
    **Ready to revolutionize your GitHub analytics?** 🚀 
    
    Start exploring the endpoints below and unlock insights you never knew existed!
  version: 0.1.22
  contact:
    name: GitHub Insight Engine Support
    url: https://github.com/org/gh-insight-engine
  license:
    name: MIT
    url: https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT
  
servers:
  - url: http://localhost:3000/api
    description: Serveur de développement
  - url: https://api.gh-insight-engine.com/api
    description: Serveur de production

security:
  - BearerAuth: []
  - {}

paths:
  /health:
    get:
      summary: Health check du service
      description: Vérifie l'état de santé de l'API et retourne des informations système
      operationId: healthCheck
      tags:
        - System
      security: []
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Service en fonctionnement
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HealthResponse'

  /ping:
    get:
      summary: Test de connectivité simple
      description: Test de connectivité basique pour vérifier que l'API répond
      operationId: ping
      tags:
        - System
      security: []
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Pong
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/PingResponse'

  /auth/login:
    post:
      summary: "🚀 Lightning-Fast GitHub Authentication"
      description: |
        # 🔐 Secure Authentication in Under 2 Seconds
        
        Transform your GitHub token into a powerful analytics key! Our ultra-fast authentication system gets you up and running in no time.
        
        ## 🎯 Why Our Auth is Different
        
        - ⚡ **Sub-second response** times
        - 🛡️ **Military-grade security** with JWT tokens  
        - 🔄 **24-hour sessions** for optimal productivity
        - 🚦 **Smart rate limiting** with graceful degradation
        - 🌍 **Global availability** with edge authentication
        
        ## 🔑 GitHub Token Setup (Super Easy!)
        
        ### Quick Setup Guide:
        
        1. **🎯 Go to GitHub** → [Settings > Tokens](https://github.com/settings/tokens) 
        2. **🆕 Create new** → Select "Classic Token"
        3. **✅ Check permissions:**
           - `repo` → 🔒 **Private repository access** (complete analysis)
           - `user` → 👤 **Profile information** (detailed insights) 
           - `read:org` → 🏢 **Organization data** (team analytics)
        4. **🎉 Copy token** → Use in the request below!
        
        ## 🚨 Pro Tips for Success
        
        - 💡 **Token expires?** Set 90+ days for best experience
        - 🔒 **Keep it secure** - Never commit tokens to code
        - 🚀 **Test immediately** after generation
        - 🎯 **Save the JWT** for all future requests
        
        ## 🎉 What You Get Back
        
        - 🎫 **Powerful JWT token** (24h validity)
        - ✅ **Permission verification** 
        - 🏆 **Access level confirmation**
        - ⚡ **Instant API readiness**
      operationId: login
      tags:
        - Authentication
      security: []
      requestBody:
        description: Identifiants de connexion
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/LoginRequest'
            example:
              username: "octocat"
              fullName: "The Octocat"
              githubToken: "ghp_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx"
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Authentification réussie
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/LoginResponse'
        '400':
          description: Données d'entrée invalides
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse'
        '401':
          description: Token GitHub invalide
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse'
        '429':
          description: Trop de tentatives de connexion
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse'

  /users/{username}:
    post:
      summary: "🎯 Intelligent Data Collection - Transform Your GitHub Profile"
      description: |
        # 🚀 One-Click Intelligence Collection
        
        **Turn your GitHub profile into a powerhouse of insights!** Our intelligent collection system analyzes every aspect of your development journey in real-time.
        
        ## ✨ What Happens During Collection
        
        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 15px 0;">
          <h3>🧠 AI-Powered Analysis Pipeline</h3>
          <p>Watch as we transform raw GitHub data into actionable intelligence!</p>
        </div>
        
        ### 📊 Data Collection Process:
        
        | Step | Duration | What We Analyze |
        |------|----------|----------------|
        | 1️⃣ **Profile Scan** | ~2s | Complete profile, reputation, expertise areas |
        | 2️⃣ **Repository Discovery** | ~5s | All repos across personal + organizations |
        | 3️⃣ **DevOps Analysis** | ~10s | CI/CD, security, quality metrics |
        | 4️⃣ **AI Processing** | ~3s | Smart insights, recommendations, trends |
        | 5️⃣ **Storage & Indexing** | ~1s | Lightning-fast future queries |
        
        ## 🎯 What You'll Discover
        
        ### 👤 **Profile Intelligence**
        - 🏆 **Developer Reputation Score** with industry percentiles
        - 📈 **Growth Trajectory** analysis and predictions  
        - 🎯 **Expertise Mapping** across technologies and domains
        - 🌟 **Community Impact** measurement and optimization tips
        
        ### 📊 **Advanced Metrics**
        - 💻 **Coding Activity Patterns** and productivity insights
        - 🔬 **Language Mastery Levels** with skill progression  
        - 🚀 **Career Progression** indicators and recommendations
        - 🎨 **Project Diversity** analysis and portfolio optimization
        
        ## 🔒 Privacy & Security
        
        - ✅ **You own your data** - collect only your own profile
        - 🛡️ **Enterprise-grade encryption** at rest and in transit
        - 🎯 **Selective visibility** - choose what to share
        - 🔄 **Smart caching** for optimal performance
        
        ## ⚡ Performance Promise
        
        - 🏃‍♂️ **Complete analysis** in under 30 seconds
        - 📱 **Real-time progress** updates via webhooks
        - 🎯 **Instant availability** for consumption endpoints
        - 🔄 **Smart incremental** updates for efficiency
      operationId: collectUserData
      tags:
        - Users
      security:
        - BearerAuth: []
      parameters:
        - name: username
          in: path
          required: true
          description: Nom d'utilisateur GitHub (doit correspondre à l'utilisateur authentifié)
          schema:
            type: string
            example: "octocat"
      responses:
        '201':
          description: Collecte des données réussie
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/CollectionResponse'
        '401':
          description: Authentification requise ou token invalide
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse'
        '403':
          description: Accès refusé - vous ne pouvez collecter que vos propres données
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse'

    get:
      summary: "⚡ Lightning-Fast Profile Insights"
      description: |
        # 🚀 Instant Access to Rich Developer Intelligence
        
        **Get comprehensive insights in under 50ms!** Access beautifully processed GitHub analytics that would take hours to compute manually.
        
        ## 🎯 Smart Access Levels
        
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin: 20px 0;">
          <div style="border: 2px solid #28a745; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px;">
            <h3>🔓 Public Access</h3>
            <p><strong>No auth required!</strong></p>
            <ul>
              <li>📊 Public repository stats</li>
              <li>🏆 Contribution highlights</li>
              <li>💫 Skills and languages</li>
              <li>🌟 Community reputation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div style="border: 2px solid #007bff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px;">
            <h3>🔒 Owner Access</h3>
            <p><strong>Full intelligence dashboard!</strong></p>
            <ul>
              <li>📈 Complete analytics suite</li>
              <li>🔬 Private repository insights</li>
              <li>🤖 AI-powered recommendations</li>
              <li>📊 Detailed performance metrics</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        ## 🎨 What You'll Get
        
        ### 📊 **Rich Response Format**
        ```json
        {
          "userProfile": {
            "reputation": "🏆 Expert Level (95th percentile)",
            "expertise": ["TypeScript", "React", "Node.js"],
            "trends": "🚀 Growing in AI/ML projects"
          },
