            "collaboration": "Strong team player"
          }
        }
        ```
        
        ### ⚡ **Performance Metrics**
        - 🏃‍♂️ **Sub-50ms response** time guaranteed
        - 📊 **Real-time data** freshness indicators  
        - 🔄 **Smart caching** with update recommendations
        - 📱 **Mobile-optimized** JSON structure
        
        ## 🎯 Perfect for Building
        
        - 🖥️ **Developer portfolios** with rich insights
        - 📊 **Team dashboards** and analytics tools
        - 🏆 **Hiring platforms** with skill assessments  
        - 📈 **Performance tracking** applications
        
        ## 💡 Pro Tips
        
        - 🔄 **Check data freshness** in the metadata
        - 🚀 **Use pagination** for large datasets
        - 📱 **Cache responses** for better UX
        - 🎯 **Combine with repositories** endpoint for complete picture
      operationId: getUserProfile
      tags:
        - Users
      security:
        - BearerAuth: []
        - {}
      parameters:
        - name: username
          in: path
          required: true
          description: Nom d'utilisateur GitHub
          schema:
            type: string
            example: "octocat"
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Données utilisateur récupérées avec succès
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/UserCompleteResponse'
        '404':
          description: Utilisateur introuvable ou données non collectées
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse'

  /summary/{username}:
    get:
      summary: "🏆 Ultimate Developer Analytics - Portfolio Ready"
      description: |
        # 🚀 The Most Comprehensive Developer Analytics Ever Built
        
        **Transform GitHub data into stunning portfolio insights!** Get publication-ready analytics perfect for CVs, portfolios, presentations, and professional profiles.
        
        ## ✨ What Makes This Endpoint Special
        
        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 15px 0;">
          <h3>🎯 Built for Professional Success</h3>
          <p>Every metric is carefully crafted for maximum impact in professional contexts!</p>
        </div>
        
        ### 🏆 **Complete Professional Profile**
        - 📊 **Reputation Scoring** (0-100) with industry percentiles
        - 🎯 **Influence Level** classification (Emerging → Visionary)
        - 💼 **Career Level** assessment with progression roadmap
        - 🌟 **Expertise Areas** with proficiency ratings
        - 📈 **Growth Trajectory** analysis and predictions
        
        ### 💻 **Technology Mastery Analysis**
        - 🔬 **Skill Categories**: Frontend, Backend, Mobile, DevOps, AI/ML, Data
        - 📊 **Proficiency Levels**: Expert (90-100%), Advanced (70-89%), Intermediate (50-69%), Beginner (0-49%)
        - 🚀 **Market Demand** scoring for each technology
        - 📈 **Learning Trends** and recommended focus areas
        - 🎯 **Technology Recommendations** based on current skills
        
        ### 🔧 **DevOps Maturity Assessment**
        - 🚀 **CI/CD Adoption** percentage across portfolio
        - 🛡️ **Security Maturity** scoring and recommendations
        - 📊 **Code Quality** metrics and improvement areas
        - 🏆 **Best Practices** adoption with industry standards
        - 📈 **Automation Score** and workflow efficiency
        
        ### 🌟 **Community Impact Metrics**
        - 🏆 **Impact Score** (0-100) with influence radius
        - ⭐ **Featured Projects** with significance ratings
        - 🎯 **Achievements** system with rarity classifications
        - 📈 **Growth Metrics** and milestone tracking
        - 👥 **Leadership Indicators** and mentoring potential
        
        ### 🎯 **Personalized Recommendations**
        - 💼 **Career Recommendations** with impact scoring
        - 🔧 **Technology Recommendations** based on market trends
        - 📚 **Learning Roadmap** with estimated timelines
        - 🚀 **Project Ideas** for portfolio enhancement
        - 🌍 **Community Engagement** opportunities
        
        ### 📊 **Industry Benchmarks**
        - 🏆 **Overall Percentile** position in the industry
        - 📈 **Category Rankings** across different skill areas
        - 🎯 **Market Position** with competitive advantages
        - 🔮 **Industry Trends** and future outlook
        
        ## 🎨 Perfect Response Format for Integration
        
        ```json
        {
          "summary": {
            "profile": {
              "reputationScore": 87,
              "influenceLevel": "Leader",
              "careerLevel": "Senior",
              "expertiseAreas": ["TypeScript", "React", "Node.js"]
            },
            "portfolioOverview": {
              "portfolioQualityScore": 92,
              "projectDiversityScore": 85,
              "totalLanguages": 12,
              "averageStarsPerRepo": 23.4
            },
            "technologyExpertise": {
              "overallExpertiseScore": 89,
              "expertLevel": [
                {
                  "technology": "TypeScript",
                  "masteryLevel": 95,
                  "marketDemand": "Very High"
                }
              ]
            },
            "recommendations": {
              "careerRecommendations": [
                {
                  "title": "Technical Leadership Role",
                  "priority": "High",
                  "potentialImpact": 90
                }
              ]
            },
            "industryBenchmarks": {
              "overallPercentile": 87,
              "marketPosition": {
                "overallRank": "Top 15%",
                "marketValue": "Senior"
              }
            }
          }
        }
        ```
        
        ## 🎯 **Access Levels**
        
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin: 20px 0;">
          <div style="border: 2px solid #28a745; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px;">
            <h3>🌍 Public Analytics</h3>
            <p><strong>No authentication required</strong></p>
            <ul>
              <li>📊 Public repository analysis</li>
              <li>🏆 Open source contributions</li>
              <li>💫 Technology expertise mapping</li>
              <li>📈 Growth trajectory insights</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div style="border: 2px solid #007bff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px;">
            <h3>🔒 Complete Intelligence</h3>
            <p><strong>Owner authentication required</strong></p>
            <ul>
              <li>📈 Real-time GitHub data</li>
              <li>🔬 Private repository insights</li>
              <li>🤖 Advanced AI recommendations</li>
              <li>📊 Comprehensive benchmarking</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        ## 🚀 **Integration Examples**
        
        ### Portfolio Website
        ```javascript
        const summary = await fetch('/api/summary/username');
        const { profile, technologyExpertise } = summary.data;
        
        // Display reputation score
        const reputation = profile.reputationScore; // 0-100
        const level = profile.influenceLevel; // "Leader"
        
        // Show technology mastery
        const expertTechs = technologyExpertise.expertLevel;
        ```
        
        ### CV/Resume Builder
        ```javascript
        const { recommendations, industryBenchmarks } = summary.data;
        
        // Career recommendations
        const nextSteps = recommendations.careerRecommendations;
        
        // Industry position
        const percentile = industryBenchmarks.overallPercentile;
        ```
        
        ## ⚡ **Performance Promise**
        
        - 🏃‍♂️ **Sub-100ms** response time for cached data
        - 📊 **Real-time calculation** for authenticated users
        - 🎯 **Instant insights** ready for display
        - 📱 **Mobile-optimized** JSON structure
        
        ## 💡 **Pro Integration Tips**
        
        - 🎨 **Visual Elements**: Use scores for progress bars and charts
        - 🏆 **Achievements**: Display achievement badges with rarity
        - 📈 **Trends**: Show growth trajectories and predictions
        - 🎯 **Recommendations**: Create action items from suggestions
        - 🌟 **Benchmarks**: Highlight industry position and rankings
      operationId: getDeveloperSummary
      tags:
        - Summary
      security:
        - BearerAuth: []
        - {}
      parameters:
        - name: username
          in: path
          required: true
          description: Nom d'utilisateur GitHub
          schema:
            type: string
            example: "octocat"
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Summary analytics ultra-complet généré avec succès
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/DeveloperSummaryResponse'
        '404':
          description: Utilisateur introuvable ou données non collectées
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse'

  /ai/{username}:
    post:
      summary: "🤖 Advanced AI Analysis - Unlock Hidden Insights"
      description: |
        # 🚀 Revolutionary AI-Powered GitHub Intelligence
        
        **Transform your GitHub data into actionable intelligence with cutting-edge AI!** Our GPT-4o-mini powered analysis engine discovers patterns, insights, and opportunities that traditional analytics miss.
        
        ## ✨ What Makes Our AI Special
        
        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 15px 0;">
          <h3>🧠 Next-Generation AI Analysis</h3>
          <p>Experience the future of developer insights with our advanced machine learning algorithms!</p>
        </div>
        
        ### 🔬 **Deep Intelligence Analysis**
        
        | Analysis Category | AI Insights | Business Value |
        |-------------------|-------------|----------------|
        | 📊 **Code Quality** | Maintainability scoring, technical debt assessment | Risk reduction, efficiency gains |
        | 🛡️ **Security Posture** | Vulnerability patterns, security best practices | Compliance, risk management |
        | 🚀 **Performance** | Build optimization, deployment efficiency | Cost reduction, speed improvement |
        | 💡 **Innovation** | Technology adoption, emerging patterns | Competitive advantage, growth |
        | 🎯 **Career Growth** | Skill gap analysis, market positioning | Professional development, hiring |
        
        ### 🎯 **What You'll Discover**
        
        #### 🏆 **Comprehensive Scoring System**
        - **Quality Score** (0-100) → Code maintainability and best practices
        - **Security Score** (0-100) → Vulnerability resilience and compliance  
        - **Innovation Score** (0-100) → Technology adoption and forward-thinking
        - **Health Score** (0-10) → Overall development ecosystem wellness
        
        #### 🔍 **Actionable Intelligence**
        - 🎯 **Personalized Recommendations** for immediate impact
        - 📈 **Growth Strategies** tailored to your profile
        - 🛡️ **Security Improvements** with priority ranking
        - 💼 **Career Advice** from industry experts (AI-powered)
        
        #### 📊 **Enterprise-Grade Metrics**
        - 🐛 **Estimated Bug Count** with severity classification
        - ⚠️ **Vulnerability Assessment** with remediation paths
        - ⏱️ **Build Time Optimization** suggestions
        - 🧪 **Test Coverage** analysis and improvement tips
        
        ## 🔒 **Privacy & Security**
        
        - ✅ **Your data, your control** - analyze only your own repositories
        - 🛡️ **Privacy-first AI** - no data retention for training
        - 🔐 **Enterprise encryption** throughout the analysis pipeline
        - 🎯 **Selective sharing** - choose what insights to make public
        
        ## ⚡ **Analysis Performance**
        
        - 🏃‍♂️ **Complete analysis** in under 30 seconds
        - 🤖 **GPT-4o-mini powered** for maximum accuracy
        - 🔄 **Smart caching** for instant re-access
        - 📱 **Real-time progress** updates via response streaming
        
        ## 💡 **Perfect For**
        
        - 👨‍💻 **Individual Developers** → Portfolio optimization, skill assessment
        - 👥 **Development Teams** → Code quality insights, security audits
        - 🏢 **Tech Recruiters** → Candidate evaluation, skill verification
        - 📊 **Engineering Managers** → Team performance, technology decisions
        
        ## 🎯 **Quick Start**
        
        ```bash
        # Launch AI analysis for your profile
        curl -X POST "https://api.gh-insight-engine.com/ai/your-username" \
             -H "Authorization: Bearer your_jwt_token" \
             -H "Content-Type: application/json"
        
        # Get results immediately after
        curl "https://api.gh-insight-engine.com/ai/your-username"
        ```
        
        **Ready to unlock your GitHub potential?** 🚀
      operationId: performAIAnalysis
      tags:
        - AI Analysis
      security:
        - BearerAuth: []
      parameters:
        - name: username
          in: path
          required: true
