  /ai/status:
    get:
      summary: "🔍 AI Service Health & Capabilities"
      description: |
        # 🤖 Real-Time AI Service Status Dashboard
        
        **Monitor our AI infrastructure and capabilities in real-time!** Get instant visibility into service health, model availability, and performance metrics.
        
        ## 🎯 **What You'll Monitor**
        
        ### 🟢 **Service Health**
        - ⚡ **Availability Status** → Real-time uptime monitoring
        - 🔗 **API Connectivity** → OpenAI integration health
        - 🧠 **Model Status** → GPT-4o-mini availability and performance
        - 📊 **Response Times** → Current latency and throughput metrics
        
        ### 🛠️ **Capabilities Overview**
        - 🔬 **Quality Analysis** → Code maintainability scoring
        - 🛡️ **Security Analysis** → Vulnerability pattern detection
        - ⚡ **Performance Analysis** → Build and deployment optimization
        - 📊 **Repository Scoring** → Individual project assessments
        - 💼 **Career Insights** → Professional development guidance
        
        ### 🚨 **Fallback Intelligence**
        - 🔄 **Smart Fallback** → Statistical analysis when AI unavailable
        - 📊 **Baseline Metrics** → Fundamental scoring always available
        - 🎯 **Graceful Degradation** → No service interruption
        
        ## 📊 **Response Structure**
        
        ```json
        {
          "service": "AI Analysis Service",
          "status": "available",
          "configuration": {
            "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
            "maxTokens": 4096,
            "temperature": 0.3
          },
          "capabilities": {
            "qualityAnalysis": true,
            "securityAnalysis": true,
            "performanceAnalysis": true,
            "repositoryScoring": true,
            "careerInsights": true
          },
          "limitations": [],
          "fallbackMode": {
            "enabled": true,
            "description": "Statistical analysis available when AI unavailable"
          }
        }
        ```
        
        ## 🎯 **Perfect for Monitoring**
        - 🖥️ **Service dashboards** → Infrastructure monitoring
        - 📱 **Mobile apps** → Feature availability checking
        - 🔔 **Alert systems** → Proactive service monitoring
        - 👥 **User interfaces** → Dynamic feature enabling/disabling
        
        ## 💡 **Pro Tips**
        - 🔄 **Check before analysis** → Verify AI availability
        - 📊 **Cache status responses** → Reduce monitoring overhead
        - 🚨 **Implement fallbacks** → Handle service degradation gracefully
        - 📈 **Track trends** → Monitor service improvement over time
      operationId: getAIServiceStatus
      tags:
        - AI Analysis
      security: []
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Statut du service IA récupéré avec succès
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/AIServiceStatusResponse'

  /repositories/{username}:
    post:
      summary: "🔧 Ultimate DevOps Intelligence Collection"  
      description: |
        # 🚀 Transform Your Repositories Into Intelligence Goldmines
        
        **The most comprehensive repository analysis engine ever built!** We dive deep into every aspect of your development ecosystem to uncover hidden insights and optimization opportunities.
        
        ## 🎯 Revolutionary Analysis Engine
        
        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b 0%, #ffa726 100%); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 15px 0;">
          <h3>🔬 Advanced Repository Intelligence</h3>
          <p>Watch us analyze hundreds of data points across your entire development portfolio!</p>
        </div>
        
        ### 🚀 Multi-Dimensional Analysis Pipeline
        
        | Phase | Duration | Intelligence Extracted |
        |-------|----------|----------------------|
        | 🔍 **Discovery** | ~5s | All repos across personal + organizations |
        | 🔧 **DevOps Scan** | ~15s | CI/CD maturity, automation levels |
        | 🛡️ **Security Audit** | ~10s | Vulnerabilities, best practices, compliance |
        | 📊 **Quality Analysis** | ~12s | Code health, maintainability, debt |
        | 🤖 **AI Enhancement** | ~8s | Insights, patterns, recommendations |
        | 💾 **Smart Indexing** | ~3s | Optimized storage for lightning queries |
        
        ## 🏆 What Makes Our Analysis Unique
        
        ### 🔧 **DevOps Maturity Assessment**
        - 🚀 **CI/CD Pipeline Analysis** - Workflow efficiency scoring
        - 📈 **Deployment Frequency** - Release cycle optimization
        - 🎯 **Lead Time Metrics** - Development velocity insights
        - 🔄 **Rollback Analysis** - Reliability and recovery patterns
        
        ### 🛡️ **Security Intelligence**
        - 🔒 **Vulnerability Assessment** - Real-time security posture
        - 📋 **Compliance Scoring** - Industry standard adherence
        - 🚨 **Alert Management** - Proactive threat monitoring
        - 🔐 **Access Control** - Permission and policy analysis
        
        ### 📊 **Code Quality Insights**
        - 🧹 **Technical Debt** - Maintenance burden quantification
        - 📈 **Complexity Metrics** - Maintainability scoring
        - 🎨 **Style Consistency** - Code standard compliance
        - 🔄 **Refactoring Opportunities** - Improvement recommendations
        
        ### 🌟 **Community Health**
        - 📖 **Documentation Quality** - README, guides, API docs
        - 🤝 **Contribution Experience** - Onboarding effectiveness
        - 🎯 **Issue Management** - Response time and resolution
        - 💬 **Community Engagement** - Activity and growth patterns
        
        ## 📈 Intelligence You'll Unlock
        
        - 🏆 **DevOps Maturity Score** (0-100) with improvement roadmap
        - 🎯 **Repository Rankings** within your portfolio
        - 📊 **Technology Stack Analysis** with future recommendations
        - 🚀 **Performance Benchmarks** against industry standards
        - 🤖 **AI-Powered Insights** for strategic decision making
        
        ## ⚡ Collection Promise
        
        - 🏃‍♂️ **Complete analysis** in under 60 seconds
        - 📱 **Real-time progress** with detailed status updates
        - 🔄 **Incremental updates** for efficiency
        - 🎯 **Zero disruption** to your development workflow
      operationId: collectRepositoriesData
      tags:
        - Repositories
      security:
        - BearerAuth: []
      parameters:
        - name: username
          in: path
          required: true
          description: Nom d'utilisateur GitHub (doit correspondre à l'utilisateur authentifié)
          schema:
            type: string
            example: "octocat"
      responses:
        '201':
          description: Collecte des repositories réussie
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/CollectionResponse'
        '401':
          description: Authentification requise ou token invalide
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse'
        '403':
          description: Accès refusé - vous ne pouvez collecter que vos propres repositories
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse'

    get:
